.         I/O Includes
. =========================================================================
.
          INC       STD001IO
          INC       OPRDEAIO/INC
          INC       PATECOIO/INC
          INC       PATMI1IO/INC
          INC       PATICOIO/INC
          INC       PMSVX1IO/INC
